{"pageProps":{"article":{"title":"Buddha Bowls Robbed By Armed Suspect","category":"News","subcategory":"Crime","publish_date":"2020-01-08T08:00:00.000Z","full_thumbnail":"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/New-Logo-Featured-e1527757142402.jpg?resize=355%2C230&ssl=1","mobile_thumbnail":"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/New-Logo-Featured-e1527757142402.jpg?resize=980%2C647&ssl=1","description":"The suspect, described as a Hispanic male in his late 20s or early 30s wearing a hooded sweatshirt and jeans, was armed and took an “undisclosed” amount of money.","content":"<div class=\"single-post-content\">\n            <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A business on the 900 block of Embarcadero Del Mar was robbed late Wednesday afternoon, according to Raquel Zick, Santa Barbara County Sheriff’s Office spokesperson. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The suspect, described as a </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hispanic male in his late 20s or early 30s wearing a hooded sweatshirt and jeans, was armed and took an “undisclosed” amount of money. He was last seen running toward Del Playa Drive. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The press release did not state the name of the business, but a Nexus reporter on the scene confirmed that the restaurant was Buddha Bowls. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The investigation remains ongoing. Anyone with information regarding this incident can call the sheriff’s office at 805-681-4171 or leave an anonymous tip </span><a href=\"https://www.sbsheriff.org/home/anonymous-tip/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">here</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span></p>\n<p><em>Sean Crommelin contributed reporting. </em></p><div class=\"h5ab-print-button-container\"><div class=\"h5ab-print-button h5ab-print-button-left\" style=\"cursor: pointer; color: #555\"><i class=\"fa fa-print fa-lg\"></i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Print</span></